# ğŸ–¥ï¸ **LEVEL 3 â€” Desktop GUI Frameworks**

You must pick **one primary GUI framework**.

## ğŸ”¹ Option A â€” **Qt (Most popular in industry)**

* Qt Widgets (Traditional desktop UI)
* Qt Quick/QML (Modern dynamic UI)
* Signals/Slots
* Models & Views
* Networking (QNetworkAccessManager)
* Multithreading with QThread
* File I/O

**You can build:** dashboards, editors, players, tools, etc.

---

## ğŸ”¹ Option B â€” wxWidgets (Open source, lightweight)

* Classic widget toolkit
* Native look on all platforms

---

## ğŸ”¹ Option C â€” Dear ImGui (Game tools, internal tools)

* Immediate mode UI
* Perfect for tools, dashboards, simulations

---

## ğŸ”¹ Option D â€” Win32 / MFC (Windows-only)

* Learn only if your job requires Windows native development.

